network_event_schema = StructType()\
.add("status", StringType())\
.add("code", StringType())\
.add("result", StructType().add("totalCount",StringType())\
                                    .add("count", StringType())\
                                    .add("entry", ArrayType(\
                                        StructType().add("name", StringType())\
                                                    .add("uuid", StringType())\
                                                    .add("source", StructType().add("member", ArrayType(StringType())))\
                                                    .add("destination", StructType().add("member", ArrayType(StringType())))\
                                                    .add("sourceUser", StructType().add("member", ArrayType(StringType())))\
                                                    .add("category", StructType().add("member", ArrayType(StringType())))\
                                                    .add("application", StructType().add("member", ArrayType(StringType())))\
                                                    .add("service", StructType().add("member", ArrayType(StringType())))\
                                                    .add("action", StringType())

                                                    
                                    )))

import json
eventHubname= "twks-nitel-eventhub"
#connectionString = "Endpoint=sb://twks-nitel-eventhub-ns.servicebus.windows.net/;SharedAccessKeyName=RootManageSharedAccessKey;SharedAccessKey=ZoiVkf7QQAokyDknOwm8znLFFN0Qz0IzX+AEhBrvSxk="
connectionString = "Endpoint=sb://twks-nitel-eventhub-ns.servicebus.windows.net/;SharedAccessKeyName=EventReaderPolicy;SharedAccessKey=AwJWaejO1DdHY2OqM9HLdWrGTTbXmzxaZ+AEhJ2FQnI="

eventHubConnectionStringWithEntity = connectionString + ";EntityPath=" + eventHubname


startingEventPosition = {
  "offset": "@latest",  
  "seqNo": -1,            #not in use
  "enqueuedTime": None,   #not in use
  "isInclusive": True
}

ehConf = {}
ehConf['eventhubs.connectionString'] = sc._jvm.org.apache.spark.eventhubs.EventHubsUtils.encrypt(eventHubConnectionStringWithEntity)

ehConf["eventhubs.startingPosition"] = json.dumps(startingEventPosition)
ehConf["eventhubs.consumerGroup"] = 'twks-nitel-consumer-group'

root_path = "abfss://twks-nitel-datalake@twksnitelstorageacc.dfs.core.windows.net/"
parquet_data_path = root_path + "/datacaptor-bronze-parquet"
delta_data_path = root_path + "/datacaptor-bronze-delta"
json_data_path = root_path + "/datacaptor-bronze-json"
checkpoint_loc = root_path + "/checkpoint-dir"
## Reading Event Hub Data from Spark Streaming

edf = spark.readStream.format("eventhubs").options(**ehConf).load()

nitel_raw_df = edf.withColumn("nitel_raw_data", col("body").cast("string")).select('properties','nitel_raw_data')

nitel_captor_data_df = nitel_raw_df.select("properties",from_json("nitel_raw_data", network_event_schema).alias("nitel_captor_data")).select("properties","nitel_captor_data.status","nitel_captor_data.code","nitel_captor_data.result.*")

explode_df = nitel_captor_data_df.select('properties','status','code','totalCount', 'count', explode("entry").alias("entry")).select(element_at('properties','id').alias("id"),element_at('properties','timestamp').alias("timestamp"),'status','code','totalCount','count','entry.*')

explode_df.printSchema

where id is not null
and action == 'allow'
    and array_contains(source.member,'any')
    and array_contains(destination.member,'any')
    and array_contains(category.member,'any')
    and array_contains(sourceUser.member,'any')
    and array_contains(application.member,'any')
    and array_contains(service.member,'any')
